title: Woodstock's Pizza - El Cajon Blvd
typeOfFood: Lacto, American, Pizza, Salad bar, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Pizzeria with multiple locations; this one is near San Diego State University. Has whole grain crust, gluten-free crust, and Daiya vegan cheese at extra charge. Choice of salads, or build your own. The garlic bread appetizer and cinnamon bread dessert are both vegan suitable.
